# Email configuration for Nodemailer
EMAIL_USER=your-email@gmail.com
EMAIL_PASS=your-app-password-or-email-password
BUSINESS_EMAIL=business-email@example.com

# Instructions:
# 1. Copy this file to .env.local
# 2. Replace the values with your actual email credentials
# 3. For Gmail, you'll need to use an App Password instead of your regular password
# 4. To generate Gmail App Password:
#    - Go to Google Account settings
#    - Enable 2-factor authentication
#    - Generate an App Password for this application
# 5. BUSINESS_EMAIL is where contact form submissions will be sent
